### Get all users
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get user by ID - Alice (ID: 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get user by ID - Bob (ID: 2)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/2
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get user by ID - Charlie (ID: 3)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/3
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get user by ID - Non-existent user (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/999
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get user with invalid ID (should return 400)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/invalid
Content-Type: application/json

